   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>	Aurelius Timotheos son of Herakleides, assistant of Seleukos, to Aurelius Aion son of Sarapion from Karanis, greeting. I have received from you the pay of an assistant in the service of the decurionate, for the twelfth indiction for three months, 3 mos. only, in full. I, Aurelius Amonios from Karanis, wrote for him. 
</ab>
